Package com.main_system

Class Competitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.main_system.Competitor
  • public class Competitor
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a competitor in the system. Stores the details of a competitor including their ID, name, competition level, age, and scores.

                  java.lang.String competitionLevel,

        competitorID - The ID of the competitor.
        name - The name of the competitor.
        competitionLevel - The competition level of the competitor.
        age - The age of the competitor.
        overallScore - The overall score for the competitor.
